                        <foliation>
                           <p>188 folios (+ 7 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
                        </foliation>
                        <collation>
                           <p>Quires of mostly 12 leaves each.</p>
                        </collation>
                        <condition>
                           <p>Damp entry at head and tidemarks.</p>
                           <p>Mould-damage at ends, with repairs.</p>
                        </condition>
